#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:1
msgid "中断与取消（AbortSignal）"
msgstr "Abort and Cancel (AbortSignal)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:3
msgid ""
"AbortSignal 是一个轻量级的中断机制，用于在运行中的 Agent 回合里停止流式输出、取消正在执行的工具调用，并尽快收敛到安全的终止状态。"
msgstr ""
"AbortSignal is a lightweight abort mechanism used to stop streaming output "
"during an ongoing Agent turn, cancel tool calls being executed, and quickly "
"converge to a safe termination state."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:5
msgid "适用场景包括："
msgstr "Applicable scenarios include:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:7
msgid "用户主动打断长回复"
msgstr "User actively interrupts long response"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:8
msgid "UI/服务端超时控制"
msgstr "UI/Server-side Timeout Control"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:9
msgid "上下文切换（先停掉旧回合，再启动新回合）"
msgstr "Context switching (first stop the old round, then start a new round)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:11
msgid "核心概念"
msgstr "Core Concept"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:13
msgid "`AbortSignal`：一个可在多个协程之间共享的中断信号。"
msgstr ""
"`AbortSignal`: an interrupt signal that can be shared among multiple "
"coroutines."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:14
msgid "`_abort_signal`：调用参数名（推荐用常量 `ABORT_SIGNAL_PARAM` 避免硬编码）。"
msgstr ""
"`_abort_signal`: call parameter name (recommended to use the constant "
"`ABORT_SIGNAL_PARAM` to avoid hardcoding)."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:15
msgid "`abort(reason)`：触发中断，并可附带原因说明。"
msgstr ""
"`abort(reason)`：Triggers an abort, optionally with a reason explanation."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:17
msgid "提示：`_abort_signal` 只用于运行时控制，不会进入 prompt，也不会传给模型或工具。"
msgstr ""
"Note: `_abort_signal` is only used for runtime control, it does not enter "
"the prompt, nor is it passed to the model or tools."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:19
msgid "基本用法"
msgstr "Basic Usage"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:21
msgid "llm_chat 示例"
msgstr "llm_chat example"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:53
msgid "llm_function 示例"
msgstr "llm_function example"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:83
msgid "运行行为"
msgstr "runtime behavior"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:85
msgid "**流式输出**：中断后不再接收新的 chunk。"
msgstr ""
"**Streaming output**: No new chunks will be received after interruption."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:86
msgid ""
"**工具调用**：正在执行的工具调用会被取消；在事件流中可能看到 `ToolCallErrorEvent`，其 `error_type` 为 "
"`CancelledError`。"
msgstr ""
"**Tool Call**: The tool call being executed will be cancelled; in the event "
"stream, you may see `ToolCallErrorEvent`, whose `error_type` is "
"`CancelledError`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:87
msgid "**事件流收尾**：当 `enable_event=True` 时，`ReactEndEvent.extra` 会包含："
msgstr ""
"**Event Stream Ending**: when `enable_event=True`, `ReactEndEvent.extra` "
"will contain:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:88
msgid "`aborted: true`"
msgstr "aborted: true"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:89
msgid "`abort_reason: <reason>`（如果传入了 reason）"
msgstr "abort_reason: <reason> (if reason was passed)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:90
msgid "**非事件流模式**：生成器会提前结束，不会额外产出 `ReactEndEvent`。"
msgstr ""
"**Non-event-stream mode**: The generator will end early and will not "
"additionally produce `ReactEndEvent`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:92
msgid "注意：AbortSignal 是协作式中断。如果工具本身不可取消或处于阻塞状态，实际停止时间可能滞后。"
msgstr ""
"Note: AbortSignal is a cooperative interruption. If the tool itself is not "
"cancelable or is in a blocked state, the actual stop time may lag."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:94
msgid "TUI 的内置中断"
msgstr "TUI built-in interrupt"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:96
msgid "在 `@tui` 场景下，当 Agent 仍在回复时再次发送消息，会自动触发中断："
msgstr ""
"In the `@tui` scenario, sending another message while the Agent is still "
"responding will automatically trigger an interruption:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:98
msgid "当前回合被中止，新的用户消息进入队列"
msgstr "Current turn was aborted, new user message enters queue"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:99
msgid "新消息会自动加上中断提示语（`\"我要打断你的回复。\"`）以引导模型及时收束"
msgstr ""
"New messages will automatically add an interruption prompt (`\"I want to "
"interrupt your response.\"`) to guide the model to conclude in a timely "
"manner."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/abort.md:101
msgid "如果你需要更细的控制（比如自定义中断提示语），可以绕过内置流程，手动创建并传入 `AbortSignal`。"
msgstr ""
"If you need finer control (for example, custom abort messages), you can "
"bypass the built-in process and manually create and pass `AbortSignal`."
